<p>Tendermint has some tools that are associated with it for:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="/main/tools/debugging.md">Debugging</a></li>
  <li><a href="#benchmarking">Benchmarking</a></li>
  <li><a href="#testnets">Testnets</a></li>
  <li><a href="./remote-signer-validation.md">Validation of remote signers</a></li>
