<h2 id="benchmarking">Benchmarking</h2>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/informalsystems/tm-load-test">https://github.com/informalsystems/tm-load-test</a></li>
</ul>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">tm-load-test</code> is a distributed load testing tool (and framework) for load
testing Tendermint networks.</p>

<h2 id="testnets">Testnets</h2>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/informalsystems/testnets">https://github.com/informalsystems/testnets</a></li>
</ul>

<p>This repository contains various different configurations of test networks for,
and relating to, Tendermint.</p>
